dc_title_s: Map of the Ashtabula River and Conneaut Creek Basins and adjacent Lake Erie tributaries showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Prepared by HENRY L. PREE, JR. Geologist, Ohio Division of Water|Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.|Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Ashtabula River and Conneaut Creek Basins and the quality of underground water.|Scale bar lower right corner.
